tourBios.curYearHigh: Finished T16 at the PGA Professional Championship to earn an invite to the PGA Championship at Whistling Straits in Wisconsin.
tourBios.carHigh:
2014: Finished T6 at the New England PGA Section Championship...Added a T3 at the New England PGA Assistants' Championship.

2012: Won the New England PGA Assistants' Fall Championship.
tourBios.personal: Is an assistant professional at the Myopia Hunt Club in South Hamilton, Mass...Has recorded four career holes-in-one...Played 121 holes in one day during the 2011 Ouimet Golf Marathon to raise college scholarship funds for Ouimet Award recipients.
